From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: sarun <noreply@sarun>
Date: Fri, 17 Jul 2026 00:32:34 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Share decoder with raw FUSE transport

Accept caller-owned kernel FUSE request and reply buffers through the same opcode dispatch used for virtqueue descriptors. Keep zero-copy byte movement transport-specific while retaining one filesystem protocol implementation.

---
